## Cry Detection & Mother Voice Response Module

| Component          | Connection                    |
| ------------------ | ----------------------------- |
| LM393 Sound Sensor | Sound Detection Input         |
| DFPlayer Mini      | Audio Playback                |
| MicroSD Card       | Stores Mother Voice Recording |
| Speaker            | Audio Output                  |
| TP4056 Module      | Battery Charging              |
| Lithium Battery    | Power Supply                  |

### Working

* LM393 continuously monitors sound.
* When baby crying is detected, DFPlayer Mini is activated.
* DFPlayer Mini plays pre-recorded mother's voice through the speaker.
* Helps calm the infant until caregivers respond.

